  place from Nov 28, 2020 to Jan 06, 2021 at the ATTO heliport. This
  is a small clearing ($2{,}400\,\mathrm{m^2}$) that allowed 4 short
  (7.2 m high) scaffolding towers to be erected.  Each tower platform
  measured $1.7 \times 1.3 \mathrm{m^2}$. The towers were placed 8 m appart from
