  \includegraphics[width=0.8\textwidth]{fig02-n.pdf}
  \caption{Wind direction distribution of the 22.5\degree-wide
    (360\degree/16) sector median velocity vector before (blue) and
    after (red) the planar fit rotation. The black continuous curves
