    fit.\label{fig:tilt}}
\end{figure}



Figure \ref{fig:tilt} also shows the comparison between the tilt
values evaluated before and after the planar fit. The improvement is
apparent, particularly over those wind sectors that displayed the
largest departures from the fitted sinusoids. Note that for some
directions there are still large values, but this is mostly due to a
